    <remarks>
      <format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="7aa86-103">当对方法进行调用 <xref:System.Threading.Thread.Abort%2A> 以销毁线程时，公共语言运行时将引发 <xref:System.Threading.ThreadAbortException> 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7aa86-103">When a call is made to the <xref:System.Threading.Thread.Abort%2A> method to destroy a thread, the common language runtime throws a <xref:System.Threading.ThreadAbortException>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7aa86-104"><xref:System.Threading.ThreadAbortException> 是一个可以被捕获的特殊异常，但会在块的末尾再次自动引发 `catch` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7aa86-104"><xref:System.Threading.ThreadAbortException> is a special exception that can be caught, but it will automatically be raised again at the end of the `catch` block.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7aa86-105">引发此异常时，运行时会在 `finally` 结束线程之前执行所有块。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7aa86-105">When this exception is raised, the runtime executes all the `finally` blocks before ending the thread.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7aa86-106">因为线程可以在块中执行未绑定的计算 `finally` 或调用 <xref:System.Threading.Thread.ResetAbort%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> 以取消中止，所以不能保证线程永远就会结束。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7aa86-106">Because the thread can do an unbounded computation in the `finally` blocks or call <xref:System.Threading.Thread.ResetAbort%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> to cancel the abort, there is no guarantee that the thread will ever end.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7aa86-107">如果要等到中止的线程结束，则可以调用 <xref:System.Threading.Thread.Join%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> 方法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7aa86-107">If you want to wait until the aborted thread has ended, you can call the <xref:System.Threading.Thread.Join%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> method.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7aa86-108"><xref:System.Threading.Thread.Join%2A> 在线程实际停止执行之前，不会返回阻止调用。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7aa86-108"><xref:System.Threading.Thread.Join%2A> is a blocking call that does not return until the thread actually stops executing.</span></span>  
  
<span data-ttu-id="7aa86-109">**仅适用于 .Net Core：** 尽管 .NET Core 中存在此类型，但由于 <xref:System.Threading.Thread.Abort%2A> 不支持，公共语言运行时将不会引发 <xref:System.Threading.ThreadAbortException> 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7aa86-109">**.NET Core only:** Even though this type exists in .NET Core, since <xref:System.Threading.Thread.Abort%2A> is not supported, the common language runtime won't ever throw <xref:System.Threading.ThreadAbortException>.</span></span>

> [!NOTE]
>  <span data-ttu-id="7aa86-110">如果公共语言运行时 (CLR) 在托管的可执行文件中的所有前台线程结束后停止后台线程，则不会使用 <xref:System.Threading.Thread.Abort%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7aa86-110">When the common language runtime (CLR) stops background threads after all foreground threads in a managed executable have ended, it does not use <xref:System.Threading.Thread.Abort%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7aa86-111">因此，您不能使用 <xref:System.Threading.ThreadAbortException> 来检测由 CLR 终止后台线程的时间。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7aa86-111">Therefore, you cannot use <xref:System.Threading.ThreadAbortException> to detect when background threads are being terminated by the CLR.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="7aa86-112"><xref:System.Threading.ThreadAbortException> 使用 HRESULT COR_E_THREADABORTED，其值为0x80131530。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7aa86-112"><xref:System.Threading.ThreadAbortException> uses the HRESULT COR_E_THREADABORTED, which has the value 0x80131530.</span></span>  
  
> [!NOTE]
>  <span data-ttu-id="7aa86-113">继承属性的值 <xref:System.Exception.Data%2A> 始终为 `null` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7aa86-113">The value of the inherited <xref:System.Exception.Data%2A> property is always `null`.</span></span>  
  
   
  
